Introduction

Lin Lin (Korean: 린린; Japanese: リンリン; Chinese: 粼粼) is a Taiwanese singer, dancer and rapper under HIM International Music, formerly under FNC Entertainment. She is a member of the Taiwanese girl group babyMINT and is a former member and the Lead Dancer, Sub Vocalist and Sub Rapper of the South Korean girl group Cherry Bullet.

On January 21, 2019, she made her official debut as a member of the South Korean girl group Cherry Bullet with the single mini album "Let's Play Cherry Bullet" with "Q & A" serving as the title track.
